'''Compostable packaging''' consists of [[paper]], [[compostable plastic]] and other fully [[biodegradable]] materials.

All [[packaging]] for food sold at the [[Sydney 2000 Olympic Games]]{{w|2000 Summer Olympics}} was [[compost]]able, making for [[green]]er [[waste management]] for this large-scale [[event]].

